problem_data.title: Add Digits
problem_data.description: Given an integer num, repeatedly add all its digits until the result has only one digit, and return it.

examples.explanation:
The process is
38 --> 3 + 8 --> 11
11 --> 1 + 1 --> 2
Since 2 has only one digit, return it.

experiment_result.error: AI 未生成任何有效測資
